room_title: Escape room "The Albino Elephant" by Mental Mansion in Eugene
room_description: Exotic Eugene’s Traveling Circus is coming to town but you'd better hold on to your valuables! A group of thieves is traveling the country disguised as performers and committing high-end heists. You and your team of investigators are the FBI's last hope to catch these clowns - literally in the act! Find the evidence and make your уscape before the final curtain falls...
